<br>
Also, having a druid in CT is pointless.  Sure you get evac, as you'll probably need it with the shitty dps you'll get with ruining a slot there with a druid.  I have a couple druid friends with lvl 60 and tons of good gear and aa points that won't set foot in CT because they won't get grouped.<br>
<br>
In closing, unless you bring your own group to mess around at IZ, don't go there unless you are 60.  You won't kill fast enough to have fun, you'll train IZ with AE mobs that kill monks FD and peeps invis and afk at IZ, and pretty much get owned there. <p>Labbats Brew <BR>
